Content: [dscrdeql] <Biomech-Founder> UTXO is and unspent transaction. Coin control was introduced in Proof of Stake wallets, and then in Bitcoin core so you could pick and choose, primarily to avoid fees and maximize POS returns. Atomic swaps match order to specific UTXO's rather than order size.
